 Why would someone use ODCR?
----------------------------------------------
During Black Friday / app launches â†’ need guaranteed scaling
For DR (Disaster Recovery)
For regulatory requirements (banks, government)
Ensures capacity during region/zone shortages

 Why would someone use ML Capacity Blocks?
-----------------------------------------------
GPU shortages are common
Deep learning training needs stable GPU cluster
You book capacity exactly when needed





